			"classSource": "PHB",
			"subclassShortName": "Arcane Ordnance",
			"subclassSource": "ArcaneOrdnanceSorcerer",
			"level": 1,
			"entries": [
				"一个强大的巫师将你，或者你的祖先，转化成了一把活生生的奥术武器。他们想要一个忠诚的士兵，能够用简单但毁灭性的力量消灭他们的敌人。然而，他们严重低估了他们创造物的力量和对自治的渴望。",
				{
					"type": "refSubclassFeature",
					"subclassFeature": "Arsenal Spells|Sorcerer|PHB|Arcane Ordnance|ArcaneOrdnanceSorcerer|1"
				},
				{
					"type": "refSubclassFeature",
					"subclassFeature": "Mystic Artillery|Sorcerer|PHB|Arcane Ordnance|ArcaneOrdnanceSorcerer|1"
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"name": "Arsenal Spells",
			"source": "ArcaneOrdnanceSorcerer",
			"className": "Sorcerer",
			"classSource": "PHB",
			"subclassShortName": "Arcane Ordnance",
			"subclassSource": "ArcaneOrdnanceSorcerer",
			"level": 1,
			"header": 1,
			"entries": [
				"{@i 1st-level Arcane Ordnance feature}",
				"你体内注入的魔法是为了对抗法师和战士而设计的。你在下表中标有的巫师等级上学会某些法术。它们对你来说算是巫师法术，但不会计入你已知法术的数量。(sorcerer)",
				{
					"type": "table",
					"caption": "Arsenal Spells",
					"colLabels": [
						"Sorcerer Level",
						"Spells"
					],
					"colStyles": [
						"col-2 text-center",
						"col-10"
					],
					"rows": [
						[
							"1st",
							"{@spell mage armor}, {@spell magic missile}, {@spell shield}"
						],
						[
							"3rd",
							"{@spell darkness}, {@spell silence}"
						],
						[
							"5th",
							"{@spell counterspell}, {@spell fly}"
						],
						[
							"7th",
							"{@spell dimension door}, {@spell otiluke's resilient sphere||resilient sphere}"
						],
						[
							"9th",
							"{@spell bigby's hand||arcane hand}, {@spell wall of force}"
						]
					]
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"name": "Mystic Artillery",
			"source": "ArcaneOrdnanceSorcerer",
			"className": "Sorcerer",
			"classSource": "PHB",
			"subclassShortName": "Arcane Ordnance",
			"subclassSource": "ArcaneOrdnanceSorcerer",
			"level": 1,
			"header": 1,
			"entries": [
				"{@i 1st-level Arcane Ordnance feature}",
				"你是一股纯净奥术力量的源泉。你可以将{@spell magic missile}作为零级战法施放。以这种方式施放时，它只会创造一个飞镖。当你达到一定的巫师等级时，飞镖的数量会增加，5级时增加到两个，11级时增加到三个，17级时增加到四个。"
			]
		},
		{
			"name": "Power Flux",
			"source": "ArcaneOrdnanceSorcerer",
			"className": "Sorcerer",
			"classSource": "PHB",
			"subclassShortName": "Arcane Ordnance",
			"subclassSource": "ArcaneOrdnanceSorcerer",
			"level": 6,
			"header": 2,
			"entries": [
				"{@i 6th-level Arcane Ordnance feature}",
				"你的法术非常适应性强。每当你完成一次长休，你可以用另一个选择替换你已掌握的任一魔法技艺 {@filter Metamagic|optionalfeatures|Feature Type=MM}，选项与你的选择相符。",
				"你还会获得一些特殊的魔法点数，数量等于你的熟练加值。这些魔法点数不能与你的魔法源泉特性一起使用，也不能用于{@spell magic missile}以外的法术的变形魔法。当你施放{@spell magic missile}时，你可以花费1点魔法点数，按照你的选择以以下一种方式修改它：",
				{
					"type": "entries",
					"name": "Seeking",
					"entries": [
						"每支飞镖可以瞄准一个看不见的生物，只要你仍然能探测到它的位置。"
					]
				},
				{
					"type": "entries",
					"name": "Shattering",
					"entries": [
						"每支飞镖可以瞄准并伤害一个未被穿戴或携带的物体。(D&D)"
					]
				},
				{
					"type": "entries",
					"name": "Shifting",
					"entries": [
						"你可以将每支飞镖的伤害类型更改为你选择的其他伤害类型。"
					]
				},
				{
					"type": "entries",
					"name": "Shoving",
					"entries": [
						"被至少一支飞镖击中的生物必须成功进行一次力量豁免检定，否则将被推动至你选择的水平方向上最多10英尺的距离。 (D&D运行组规则)"
					]
				},
				{
					"type": "entries",
					"name": "Staggering",
					"entries": [
						"被两支或更多飞镖击中的生物必须进行一次力量豁免检定，否则会倒地{@condition prone}。 (D&D 运行组)"
					]
				},
				{
					"type": "entries",
					"name": "Swarming",
					"entries": [
						"你每个插槽等级以上使用该法术时，额外创造两支飞镖而不是一支。(dnd running group rules)"
					]
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"name": "Unstoppable Force",
			"source": "ArcaneOrdnanceSorcerer",
			"className": "Sorcerer",
			"classSource": "PHB",
			"subclassShortName": "Arcane Ordnance",
			"subclassSource": "ArcaneOrdnanceSorcerer",
			"level": 14,
			"header": 2,
			"entries": [
				"{@i 14th-level Arcane Ordnance feature}",
				"你拥有的魔法超越了物理界限。当你施放1级或更高级的法术时，你可以进行一次DC 18的魅力检定，以将其施放到遮挡物后的目标上，绕过其保护效果。失败时：",
				{
					"type": "list",
					"items": [
						"如果法术以一个起始点为目标，那么该起始点将移动到障碍物的近侧。 (DND运行组规则)",
						"如果这个法术的目标是一个生物或物体，那么它会失败。",
						"如果法术产生范围效果，则被完全掩盖所阻挡。(DND运行组规则)"
					]
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"name": "Mana Barrage",
			"source": "ArcaneOrdnanceSorcerer",
			"className": "Sorcerer",
			"classSource": "PHB",
			"subclassShortName": "Arcane Ordnance",
			"subclassSource": "ArcaneOrdnanceSorcerer",
			"level": 18,
			"header": 2,
			"entries": [
				"{@i 18th-level Arcane Ordnance feature}",
				"你可以释放全部力量进行一次压倒性攻击。当你施放{@spell magic missile}时，你可以消耗5个或更多的法术点来创建同样数量的额外飞镖，并忽略任何会导致生物不受其影响的效果，比如{@creature Tarrasque||Tarrasque's} 反光甲壳或{@spell shield} 法术。"
			]
		}
	]
}
